CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 29, 1946, pg. 22, reads: "From Higher Institutions - Having completed their training in institutions of higher learning, these students are prepared to take over the job of teaching the younger generation... The right photo includes left to right: Miss Emilene Hall, Miss Hazel Thomas, Miss Marian Vaughn, Miss Cl[illegible] Berry, Miss Wilma Vaughn, twin of Marian, and Miss Sarah Jordan..."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh graduates Emilene Hall, Hazel Thomas, Marian Vaughn, Ms Berry, Wilma Vaughn, and Sarah Jordan posed with diplomas in front of Cathedral of Learning, Oakland
